trans-unit.source: Defines the method that a designer-host must implement to provide URL reference look-up for embedded resources.
trans-unit.target: Angir metoden som designer-vert må implementere for å oppgi URL-adressen referanse oppslag for innebygde ressurser.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET version 2.0 provides the ability to retrieve embedded resources from an assembly for controls, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> control.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET-versjon 2.0 gjør mulighet å hente innebygde ressurser fra en samling for kontroller som den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page>

trans-unit.source: At run time, the URL to the embedded resource can be retrieved using the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> class.
trans-unit.target: Ved kjøretid, kan URL-adressen til den innebygde ressursen hentes ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>metoden for <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: To provide a design-time means for generating a resource URL from an assembly, designer hosts can offer a service that implements the IResourceUrlGenerator interface.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verter kan tilby en tjeneste som implementerer grensesnittet IResourceUrlGenerator for å gi en utformingen betyr for å generere en URL-adresse for ressursen fra en samling.

trans-unit.source: For more information: - On using resources in localization, see [ASP.NET Web Page Resources Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon: - på ved hjelp av ressurser i lokalisering, se [ASP.NET nettsiden ressurser oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: - On using embedded resources, see [NIB:How to: Use Resources to Set Property Values in Web Server Controls](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d8e0e5c0-1958-422b-b4f5-ebe63f6c45cb) and [How to: Retrieve Resource Values Programmatically](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: – Om hvordan du bruker innebygde ressurser, kan du se [NIB: slik: Bruk ressurser til å angi egenskapsverdier i Server webkontroller](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d8e0e5c0-1958-422b-b4f5-ebe63f6c45cb) og [slik: hente ressurs-verdier programmatisk](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: - On control designers, see [ASP.NET Control Designers Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: – Om kontrollen verktøy, kan du se [ASP.NET kontrollen utviklere oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The IResourceUrlGenerator interface has one method, the <xref:System.Web.UI.IResourceUrlGenerator.GetResourceUrl%2A> method, that returns a URL reference to a resource given the resource type and name.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IResourceUrlGenerator har en metode i <xref:System.Web.UI.IResourceUrlGenerator.GetResourceUrl%2A>metode som returnerer en URL-referanse til en ressurs ressurstype og navn.</xref:System.Web.UI.IResourceUrlGenerator.GetResourceUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns a URL reference to an embedded resource in an assembly that is used at design time.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en URL-adressen referanse til en innebygd ressurs i en samling som brukes under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: At run time, the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A> method returns a URL to a resource.
trans-unit.target: Under kjøring av <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>metoden returnerer en URL-adresse til en ressurs.</xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Handlers.AssemblyResourceLoader> class defines the HTTP handler that is used to load embedded resources.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Handlers.AssemblyResourceLoader>klassen definerer HTTP-behandling som brukes til å laste inn innebygde ressurser.</xref:System.Web.Handlers.AssemblyResourceLoader>

trans-unit.source: At design time, the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> class detects design mode and delegates to the designer-host service implementation, which returns a URL.
trans-unit.target: Under utformingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>-metoden for den <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>klassen oppdager utformingsmodus og representant til vertstjenesten for designer-implementering, som returnerer en URL-adresse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager.GetWebResourceUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The type in the assembly that contains the embedded resource.
trans-unit.target: Type i samlingen som inneholder den innebygde ressursen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the resource to retrieve.
The URL reference to the resource.
